<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Box垂直方向的距离由margin决定。属于同一个BFC的两个相邻Box的margin会发生重叠</title>
    <style>
        p {
            color: #f55;
            background: #fcc;
            width: 200px;
            line-height: 100px;
            text-align:center;
            margin: 100px;
        }
        .wrap {
            overflow: hidden;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<p>Haha</p>
<div class="wrap">
<p>Hehe</p>
    <div>
</body>
</html>